# Fullstack standards (portal UI)

1. **Authoritative skill:** `.cursor/skills/senior-dotnet-angular-fullstack/SKILL.md` — layout order, spacing system, smart/dumb split, anti-patterns, response behavior.
2. **Angular + PrimeNG + tokens:** `.cursor/rules/angular-frontend.mdc` (mandatory shared UI, reactive forms, responsive rules).
3. **Figma / tokens:** `.cursor/rules/figma-design-system.mdc` when implementing visual changes.

